    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/068fa0b1e62aee277e5c5b911951e9ae.poster.avif?t=1749655257\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/068fa0b1e62aee277e5c5b911951e9ae.webm?t=1749655257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/068fa0b1e62aee277e5c5b911951e9ae.mp4?t=1749655257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某个夜晚，你平静的生活被打破，一位朋友将你引入迷雾笼罩的森林，揭开了尘封已久的黑暗。你被卷入一个充满秘术、古老生物与超自然力量的世界，必须穿越恐怖的地牢，揭开黑暗仪式背后的真相。越深入，你越意识到自己并非旁观者，而是今夜猎物中的核心。你的选择将决定命运，必须在为时已晚之前解开古老仪式的秘密。你能逃离这血染的诅咒，还是会成为它的下一个牺牲品？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验一个动态且视觉丰富的叙事。</strong>故事中的每一个时刻和转折都有独特的插图，让你沉浸在对每一个行动和情感变化都做出反应的世界中。补充这一体验的是多样化的音乐配乐，反映了旅程中的每一个曲折。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/0c0870b51ff40869b080b3cbb53548fa.poster.avif?t=1749655257\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/0c0870b51ff40869b080b3cbb53548fa.webm?t=1749655257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/0c0870b51ff40869b080b3cbb53548fa.mp4?t=1749655257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结交朋友，面对敌人，质疑周围人的真实意图。</strong>你能否识别他们的真正动机，并做出正确的选择来确保自己的生存？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/dfa90441856ac9d33ea174f212434a92.avif?t=1749655257\" width=616 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入我们的Discord社区，及时了解游戏的开发动态，并获取独家内容。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/3e0e1197abed65da36dcd3b16f875804.avif?t=1749655257\" width=616 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>聆听为这部小说精心创作的音乐。</strong>管弦乐配乐为游戏世界带来生机，既有欢快乐观的曲调，也有不祥的预示性作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136910/extras/add8990b3ae5b0c4a8bf79244956a7d3.avif?t=1749655257\" width=616 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续关注更新，并准备好沉浸在《Sanguis：遗忘者的面纱》中。</p>",
